OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,FSue Turner was just a teenager when
OL,7,Fshe was forced to give up her daughter
OL,8,Fand told ITV News Social Affairs
OL,9,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker that it
OL,10,F'ruined her life'
OL,12,FSue Turner was just 17 in 1966, when
OL,13,Fshe discovered she was pregnant, a
OL,14,Fsecret she has kept for most of her
OL,15,Flife.
