OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,F"Suddenly, I allocated a social worker
OL,7,Fwho basically told me that I'd caused
OL,8,Fmy parents enough anguish and upset
OL,9,Fand I owed it to them to wipe the
OL,10,Fslate clean, to give the baby up for
OL,11,Fadoption and start all over again,"
OL,12,Fshe told ITV Tonight.
OL,14,FShe was sent away to a mother and baby
OL,15,Fhome run by the Church of England in
OL,16,FDorking. Half a century on, the trauma
OL,17,Fof what happened there has never left
OL,18,Fher.
