OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,F"My mum told this story about me going
OL,7,Fup to Birmingham and going on a
OL,8,Fsecretarial course," Sue said.
OL,10,FShe spent nearly three months in the
OL,11,Fmother and baby home and describes
OL,12,Fbeing 'institutionalised' and
OL,13,F'expected to clean' when heavily
OL,14,Fpregnant.
OL,16,F"We had to do a lot of praying and ask
OL,17,Fa lot of forgiveness," Sue said.
