OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,FDenied pain relief and forced to give
OL,7,Fbirth alone, the cruelty continued
OL,8,Fafter labour when she was told she
OL,9,Fcould not breastfeed her daughter as
OL,10,Fit was felt she would "get too
OL,11,Fattached".
OL,13,FBecause she was unmarried, she was
OL,14,Fdeemed unfit to bring up a child. Her
OL,15,Fdaughter was taken from her and put up
OL,16,Ffor adoption.
