OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,FShe is among an estimated 200,000
OL,7,Fwomen who gave birth in homes for
OL,8,Funmarried mothers run by the church or
OL,9,Fstate, and were pressured to put their
OL,10,Fbabies up for adoption in the 40 years
OL,11,Fafter World War Two.
OL,13,FAfter contacting ITV News after seeing
OL,14,Four ongoing investigation, this is the
OL,15,Ffirst time Sue, who is 77, has ever
OL,16,Fspoken publicly about the trauma that
OL,17,Fhas cast a long shadow over her life.
