OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,F"I don't really know the person I was
OL,7,Fthen, I can still feel her pain. And
OL,8,Fall I wanted to do was to know that
OL,9,FI'd done the right thing," she said.
OL,11,F"You never heal, it's always there.
OL,12,FThat one decision which was made for
OL,13,Fme ... just ruined my life."
OL,15,FDr Michael Lambert from Lancaster
OL,16,FUniversity has spent a decade
OL,17,Fexamining these institutions including
OL,18,Fhow they were funded and operated.
