OL,3,C'It's ruined my life': Mother's trauma
OL,4,Cbeing forced to give up baby
OL,6,FHe described how unmarried mothers
OL,7,Fwere treated as 'second class' and
OL,8,Fweren't entitled to the same level of
OL,9,Fhealth treatment, social security or
OL,10,Fhousing as married women.
OL,12,FWomen in the homes were told 'to put
OL,13,Fthis shameful episode behind you and
OL,14,Fyour life will continue. They had no
OL,15,Fautonomy, they had no voice,' he said.
OL,17,FThe trauma of what happened to so many
OL,18,Fhas been passed down the generations.
