OL,6,FIn response to our programme the
OL,7,FChurch of England said: "We are deeply
OL,8,Fsaddened to hear these painful and
OL,9,Fdistressing accounts of women and
OL,10,Ffamilies who have been affected by
OL,11,Fmother and baby homes, including those
OL,12,Fwith connections to the Church of
OL,13,FEngland.
OL,15,F"To those who have suffered, we once
OL,16,Fagain offer our heartfelt sorrow and
OL,17,Fregret.
